ããã modules/           # Microfrontends shared and native modules
ããã screens/           # Page-level (Hook Component pattern)
ããã services/          # Domain logic (SOLID layout)
ã   ããã api/           # HTTP layer (Axios/Fetch)
ã   ããã class/         # Class with logical requests
ã   ããã hooks/         # Specific service hooks
ã   ããã repository/    # Data abstraction & mapping
ã   ããã services/      # Business orchestration
ã   ããã storage/       # Storage orchestration with cache or not
ã   ããã store/         # Zustand slices (only)
ã   ããã models/        # Domain types & contracts
ã   ããã utils/         # Reusable service helps
ã   ããã index.ts       # Public exports
ããã hooks/             # Cross-cutting React hooks
ããã routes/            # Navigation config
