  store/: airlineMiles.store.ts, extract.store.ts, parameter.store.ts, permission.store.ts, slices.ts
  hooks/: useAirlineMiles.ts, usePermission.ts
  utils/: cleanup.ts, participantId.ts

================================================================================
BUG TO FIX
================================================================================

File: src/services/utils/cleanup.ts

Current (BROKEN):
```typescript
export function clearRewardsProgramStore() {
  const {
    parameterPointsProgramActions,
    rewardPermissionActions,
    airlineMilesActions,
  } = useRootStore.getState();

